<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Reporting</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            background-color: #f3f4f6;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }

        .container {
            max-width: 800px;
            margin: 50px auto;
            padding: 20px;
            background-color: #ffffff;
            border-radius: 10px;
            box-shadow: 0px 0px 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }

        h1 {
            color: #333333;
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }

        p {
            font-size: 18px;
            line-height: 1.6;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }

        b {
            color: #007bff;
        }

        p:last-child {
            margin-bottom: 0;
        }

        .highlight {
            background-color: #f9fafb;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            border-radius: 5px;
            margin-top: 30px;
        }

        .highlight p {
            margin-bottom: 0;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <h1>Hello! Thank you for updating your data! Our team will contact you soon.</h1>
        <p>Weather: <b>{{plantdata.weather}}</b></p>
        <p>Temperature: <b>{{plantdata.temperature}}Â°C</b></p>
        <p>Watered: <b>{{plantdata.watered}}</b></p>
        <p>Fertilized: <b>{{plantdata.fertilized}}</b></p>
        <p>Height: <b>{{plantdata.height}}cm</b></p>
        <p>Health Condition: <b>{{plantdata.healthCondition}}</b></p>
        <p>Diseases: <b>{{plantdata.diseases}}</b></p>
        <p>Pruning: <b>{{plantdata.pruning}}</b></p>
        <p>Repotting: <b>{{plantdata.repotting}}</b></p>   
        <center><button >OK</button></center>

        <div class="highlight">
            <h2>Important Notice</h2>
            <p>Please make sure to follow the recommendations provided for optimal plant care.</p>
            <p>If you have any questions, feel free to contact our support team.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
